To use this overlay:

1) Add http://source.sjkwi.com.au/hg/gentoo-overlay/raw-file/tip/overlay.xml to 
   your list of overlay definitions files in layman.cfg. It should resemble this:

     overlays  : http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/overlays/layman-global.txt
                 http://source.sjkwi.com.au/hg/gentoo-overlay/raw-file/tip/overlay.xml

2) Tell layman to resync its overlay lists, and then fetch the sjkwi overlay:

     layman -L
     layman -a sjkwi

3) Profit!
